text:
Perry Street, at and adjoining the S.W. corner of Greenwich Street, Nos. 132-134 Perry Street, adjoining the S.W. corner of Greenwich Street, is the Old Perry Street Methodist Episcopal Chapel.

About 1915.

729 Greenwich Street, adjoining the S. E. corner of Perry Street. The archway shown leads to a center garden and from which the interior apartments are reached; there being several rear houses.

March 31, 1940

George D. Chinn
